title: Smith and Deli
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Fast food, Take-out, Israeli
description: From the owners of Smith & Daughters, comes this deli and sandwich shop which is loosely based on a traditional New York-style Jewish deli except that the food is all vegan. Opened Jun 2015. Expect pastries, sandwiches, coffee, bagels, groceries, ready-to-go meals.
